<h2>Legend</h2>
<p>
<span class="people">People</span> appear in blue.<br />
<span class="coderelease">Code Releases</span> appear in gray.<br />
<span class="commercial">Commercial</span> appear in black.<br />
<span class="event">Events</span> appear in dark green.<br />
<span class="partner">Partners</span> appear in larger purple.<br />
<span class="othertype">Others</span> appear in italic.<br />
</p>
</div>

<div class="span4">
<h2>Colophon</h2>
<p>
This page feeds the
<a href="https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/10ypjj1ofXYTtshH96qwyS9XvRNDDyvrwaCJSKjewiYQ/edit#gid=8">GeoNode Timeline Spreadsheet</a> 
into a <a href="http://simile.mit.edu/timeline/">Simile Timeline widget</a>. 
It is based on the work of <a href="http://kiyo.wordpress.com/2007/04/29/google-spreadsheet-json-to-timeline/">Kiyohito Yamamoto</a>.
You can find the source for this at <a href="https://github.com/OpenTechStrategies/timelines">GitHub</a>
</p>
